OL,5,CGUARD URGED FOR ANCIENT FOOTPRINTS     
OL,7, Footprints found on an Irish island    
OL,8, indicating animal life dating back     
OL,9, nearly 400 million years may get round-
OL,10, the-clock security.                    
OL,11,F                                       
OL,12, The prehistoric amphibian footprints   
OL,13, were discovered by Swedish geologists  
OL,14, in 1994 on Valentia Island, Co Kerry.  
OL,16, The fossilised marks are thought to be 
OL,17, among the oldest ever discovered. Now  
OL,18, experts say urgent measures are needed 
OL,19, to protect them.                       
