OL,5,CNATIONAL TRUST TO KEEP HUNT BAN        
OL,7, The National Trust's ruling council    
OL,8, has decided to keep in place a ban on  
OL,9, deer-hunting with hounds on its land.  
OL,11,GThe review came after a High Court     
OL,12,Gjudge said he believed the Trust's     
OL,13,Goriginal decision, passed in April, had
OL,14,Gbeen taken without proper consultation.
OL,15,G                                       
OL,16, The ban came after a report concluded  
OL,17, deer suffered unacceptable stress in   
OL,18, the chase. But these findings have been
OL,19, challenged by other scientists.        
