OL,5,CENGLISH GIRL BIDS TO SAVE TIGER        
OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GSixteen-year-old Jenny Osgood, from    
OL,8,GNewquay, Cornwall, is to meet the      
OL,9,GIndian PM in a bid to help save the    
OL,10,Gtiger from extinction.                 
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,GJenny will present IK Gujral with a    
OL,13,Gpetition containing 7,000 signatures   
OL,14,Gwhen she meets him in New Delhi.       
OL,15,G                                       
OL,16,GThe trip has been arranged by the      
OL,17,GEnvironmental Investigation Agency, in 
OL,18,Gassociation with local Indian groups,  
OL,19,Gincluding Tiger Link.                  
