OL,5,CTIDY BRITAIN GROUP LAUNCHES CLEAN-UP   
OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GThe Tidy Britain Group has launched a  
OL,8,Gcampaign aimed at ridding the          
OL,9,Gcountryside of rural rubbish.          
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,GThe first phase of its Countryside     
OL,12,GOffensive is due to take place in East 
OL,13,GAnglia over the weekend.               
OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,GVolunteers are to clean up on the      
OL,16,GNorfolk Broads, police will sweep      
OL,17,Glitter from the streets of Huntingdon, 
OL,18,Gand sea scouts are set to clear an     
OL,19,Gindustrial estate in Colchester, Essex.
